thread.title: Andrew

author: Andrew
title: Andrew
text: Mine is a sophisticated industry. The Servcorp offering is competitive in respect to the scope of services and the price, on my analysis the best offering, and meets my needs and my clients needs. It is quite difficult to get an 'apples to apples' comparison. I was rigorous in comparing similar services. In the end I concluded that Servcorp services and notably the Santos Place staff are able to exceed my expectations. Subsequently, the service has not disappointed.
